This is used to render parts of the scene selectively.

If the [[GameObject]]'s /layerMask/ AND the camera's /cullingMask/ is zero then the game object will be invisible from this camera.
See [[wiki:Layers|Layers]] for more information.
SA: [[wiki:class-Camera|camera component]]
CONVERTEXAMPLE
BEGIN EX

	// Only render objects in the first layer (Default layer)

	camera.cullingMask = 1 << 0;
END EX